{%- comment -%}
  The Model Section
  Tiered creator participation options with color-coded cards
{%- endcomment -%}

<section class="section">
  <div class="section-header">
    <h2 class="section-title">The Model</h2>
    <p class="section-subtitle">JUMP IN AT WHATEVER LEVEL MAKES SENSE</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="model-intro" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto var(--space-xl); text-align: center;">
    <p class="text-large">I've launched my first Print Lab — because we're printing money.</p>
    <p class="text-muted">DØLLs can jump in at whatever level makes sense:</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="grid grid--2 grid--auto">
    
    <a href="/pages/submit?tier=1" class="card tier-card tier-card--mint">
      <div class="tier-card__label">TIER 1</div>
      <h3 class="card__title">You Submit, I Print</h3>
      <p class="card__text">Got something cunty, cheeky, or sellable? Submit through the form.</p>
      <p class="card__text">I'll get it printed, posted, marketed. <strong>80-20 split.</strong> You get 80%, I take 20%. Capitalism but democratic socialism. That 20% goes back to the house so I can keep funding shit and buying bags.</p>
    </a>
    
    <a href="/pages/submit?tier=2" class="card tier-card tier-card--green">
      <div class="tier-card__label">TIER 2</div>
      <h3 class="card__title">Launch a Store</h3>
      <p class="card__text">Want your own storefront? Let's do it.</p>
      <p class="card__text">Pay The Dolls handles backend — hosting, payments, logistics. You handle front end — brand, products, creative. <strong>Same 80-20 split.</strong></p>
    </a>
    
    <a href="/pages/submit?tier=3" class="card tier-card tier-card--silver">
      <div class="tier-card__label">TIER 3</div>
      <h3 class="card__title">Cross Market Listing</h3>
      <p class="card__text">Already running a brand or e-comm? Want to promote on the site?</p>
      <p class="card__text"><strong>DM me.</strong> We'll figure it out. Think Craigslist for DL Chasers but everyone gets paid.</p>
    </a>
    
    <a href="/pages/submit?tier=4" class="card tier-card tier-card--black">
      <div class="tier-card__label">TIER 4</div>
      <h3 class="card__title">Everyone Else</h3>
      <p class="card__text">Not a DØLL but got an idea? Cool. Submit it. I'll take a look.</p>
      <p class="card__text">The door is open. Let's see what you've got.</p>
    </a>
    
  </div>
  
  <div class="money-section" style="max-width: 700px; margin: var(--space-xl) auto 0; text-align: center; padding: var(--space-l); background: var(--light-gray); border-radius: var(--radius-md);">
    <h3 style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: var(--space-m);">Where does the money go?</h3>
    <p class="text-body">Pay The Dolls merch revenue → <strong>Verse Capital.</strong> My little VC pot for throwing money at trans artists, creators, projects, whatever I feel like funding.</p>
    <p class="text-muted mt-m">Is it officially a fund? Not yet. Currently earmarked in my bank account.</p>
    <p class="text-body mt-m"><strong>Want to invest $1 mil?</strong> We're accepting equity raises. DM me.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="cta-group mt-xl">
    <a href="/pages/submit" class="btn btn--primary">SUBMIT YOUR IDEA</a>
    <a href="/pages/become-a-doll" class="btn btn--secondary">BECOME A DØLL</a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .tier-card {
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    display: block;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .tier-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }
  
  .tier-card__label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-m);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  
  /* Tier 1 - Mint Green */
  .tier-card--mint {
    border-top: 4px solid #00FF88;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.05) 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
  }
  .tier-card--mint .tier-card__label {
    color: #00FF88;
  }
  .tier-card--mint:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.2);
  }
  
  /* Tier 2 - Phthalo Green (Default) */
  .tier-card--green {
    border-top: 4px solid #123524;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(18, 53, 36, 0.03) 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
  }
  .tier-card--green .tier-card__label {
    color: #123524;
  }
  .tier-card--green:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(18, 53, 36, 0.15);
  }
  
  /* Tier 3 - Silver/Gray */
  .tier-card--silver {
    border-top: 4px solid #888888;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(136, 136, 136, 0.05) 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
  }
  .tier-card--silver .tier-card__label {
    color: #888888;
  }
  .tier-card--silver:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(136, 136, 136, 0.2);
  }
  
  /* Tier 4 - Black */
  .tier-card--black {
    border-top: 4px solid #000000;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03) 0%, #FFFFFF 100%);
  }
  .tier-card--black .tier-card__label {
    color: #000000;
  }
  .tier-card--black:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 12px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }
</style>

